abstract: HOT SPRINGS, Va., Oct. 11. -- The woman's golf tournament commenced to-day with a qualification round, eighteen holes. Miss P. abstract: NEW HAVEN, Conn., Oct. 26. -- In spite of the game with Columbia to-morrow the Yale football team went through a stiff practice this afternoon.
